1.ELFA, GLHA, ILJA, _____, MLNA

  answer ---> KLLA
  logic ---> 2nd(L) and last letter(A) are same in all , first set(EF) , second set (GH) ....and so on


2. In a certain code, MENTION is written as LNEITNO. How is PATTERN written in that code?

answer ---> OTAETNR
logic ---> for 1st letter alone write its previous alphabet
           for remaining letter swap the two of them
  
